{"view":"article","slug":"big-pyraminx","category":"Non-WCA","subcategory":null,"topDir":"Non-WCA","title":{"en":"高阶金字塔"},"content":{"en":"<p><strong>高阶金字塔</strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image1.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>Yujian Song (宋雨键)</p><p>在正四面体的高上作两道切割面, 将高分成等距的三段, 便得到了熟悉的三阶金字塔魔方, 以下简称三阶塔. 而如果将高等距切割成多段, 就得到了高阶塔. 高阶塔与三阶塔的关系, 就如同高阶魔方与三阶魔方一样. </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image2.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image3.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image4.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image5.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>可以将高阶塔的块分成如下几部分: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image6.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image7.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image8.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>图中紫色, 绿色, 橙色块分别称为中心块, 棱块以及角块. 这样, 如果采取和正阶魔方类似的降阶法, 可以将高阶塔转化为解下面这个魔方: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image9.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>这个魔方和三阶塔稍有不同, 它的每个面中心多了中心块, 叫做金氏塔(Jing's Pyraminx). 高阶塔的降阶法, 最后都会转化为金氏塔. </p><p>金氏塔怎么复原呢? 一方面可以发现金氏塔和斜转是同构的, 另一方面, 用类似三阶塔的方法也不难复原: </p><p>首先忽略掉四个面的中心块, 当作三阶塔复原, 最后中心块只会出现两对换的情形, 由于中心块无向, 可以直接用下述两对换公式(原理见”置换与魔方(四)”): </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image10.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(L R' L' R)3\">(L R' L' R)3</span></p><p>接下来的问题便是如何将高阶塔降阶为金氏塔, 先对转动进行一些说明: </p><p><strong>转动规定</strong></p><p>仍然用L,R,U,B四个字母指代四个方向, 大写字母表示最深层的转动, 小写字母表示最浅层的转动, 小写字母前加数字表示从外向内数一定层数的转动, 用三个字母表示对应的面旋转, 如: </p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image11.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image12.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image13.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image14.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>R</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>r'</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>4r</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>URL'</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>解法</strong></p><ol><li><strong>复原中心块</strong></li></ol><p>五阶及以上的塔会需要复原中心块, 六阶及以上的塔中心块复原时会需要分离三循环. </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image15.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image16.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image17.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>阶数被3整除的塔没有正中心块(这时复原要注意确定每面中心的颜色), 而阶数模3余正负1的塔中心分别为正三角和倒三角, 但无论哪种情况, 复原中心时的顺序都是先内层后外层, 每层中先倒三角再正三角, 如上图所示. </p><p>复原倒三角块可以类比复原正阶高阶魔方的中心块, 例如下图中先复原红色面中间的倒三角: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image18.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"6l' 5l URL' 6l 5l'\">6l' 5l URL' 6l 5l'</span></p><p>再复原剩下的倒三角: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image19.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"4l BLR 4l'\">4l BLR 4l'</span></p><p>复原正三角块时会需要分离三循环, 例如六阶塔, <strong>4r 4l' 4r' 4l</strong>有如下效果: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image20.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>于是分离三循环: <strong>[4r 4l' 4r' 4l, URL] = 4r 4l' 4r' 4l URL 4l' 4r 4l 4r' URL'</strong></p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image21.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\song\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\SNAGHTML16db391.PNG\" src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image22.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image23.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"4r 4l' 4r' 4l URL 4l' 4r 4l 4r' URL'\">4r 4l' 4r' 4l URL 4l' 4r 4l 4r' URL'</span></p><p>或者也可以得到纯粹的中心块交换: <strong>(4r 4l' 4r' 4l UBR 4r 4l' 4r' 4l UBR')2</strong>(原理见”置换与魔方(五)”): </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image24.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\song\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\SNAGHTML16db391.PNG\" src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image22.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image25.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(4r 4l' 4r' 4l UBR 4r 4l' 4r' 4l UBR')2\">(4r 4l' 4r' 4l UBR 4r 4l' 4r' 4l UBR')2</span></p><p>所有的正三角块都可以用上述方法复原. </p><ol><li><strong>复原棱块</strong></li></ol><p>与正阶魔方拼棱基本没有区别, 例如: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image26.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"4r UBR ULB' UBR 4r'\">4r UBR ULB' UBR 4r'</span></p><p>又如最后两棱: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image27.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"2r U' R B' 2r'\">2r U' R B' 2r'</span></p><ol><li><strong>作为金氏塔复原并处理特殊情况</strong></li></ol><p>把四个小角转好, 就可以作为金氏塔复原了, 这时可能出现三心换的特殊情况: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image28.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>这种情况可以类比斜转的角块簇分析, 借助解master skewb中的发现, 产生这种情况是由于一个角块方向错误, 于是我们摆正角块再重新复原棱块, 即上图做<strong>2u'</strong>, 重新拼好棱块<strong>R 2u' R' 2u' R 2u' R'</strong>, 再复原棱块<strong>R U R' U R U R' U</strong>,<strong> </strong>即复原了上述三心换: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image28.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"2u' R 2u' R' 2u' R 2u' U R' U R U R' U\">2u' R 2u' R' 2u' R 2u' U R' U R U R' U</span></p><p>反向三心换逆序: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image29.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U' R U' R' U' R U' 2u R' 2u R 2u R' 2u\">U' R U' R' U' R U' 2u R' 2u R 2u R' 2u</span></p><p>至此全部复原. </p>"},"algs":["(L R' L' R)3","6l' 5l URL' 6l 5l'","4l BLR 4l'","4r 4l' 4r' 4l URL 4l' 4r 4l 4r' URL'","(4r 4l' 4r' 4l UBR 4r 4l' 4r' 4l UBR')2","4r UBR ULB' UBR 4r'","2r U' R B' 2r'","2u' R 2u' R' 2u' R 2u' U R' U R U R' U","U' R U' R' U' R U' 2u R' 2u R 2u R' 2u"],"thumb":"/stats/tutorial/media/big-pyraminx/en/image1.png","warningCount":0,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":true}
